Bank Audi Profit Rises to 262 Billion Lebanese Pounds

-- B y   I n a l   E r s a n   a n d   M a s s o u d   A .   D e r h a l l y
-- 
2011-07-20T16:07:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-20/bank-audi-profit-rises-to-262-billion-lebanese-pounds-1-.html
Bank Audi SAL-Audi Saradar Group,
the largest lender in Lebanon by assets, said first-half profit
after tax rose 12 percent from the year-earlier period.  Net income increased to 261.8 billion Lebanese pounds
($172.9 million) through June, from 233.6 billion pounds a year
earlier, the Beirut-based bank said in a statement published by
the Regulatory News Service of the London Stock Exchange today.  Total assets reached $29.1 billion and deposits reached
$25.3 billion in the first six months of the year.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Inal Ersan in Dubai at 
